                    {"format": "Welcome!", "css": "font-weight: 900;\nfont-size: 4rem;"},
                    {"format": "You’re now connected to the brain of your system.\nHaGeneral doesn’t just manage PCBs — it commands them with precision.\nEvery voltage, signal, and heartbeat is under your control.\nBuilt for reliability. Engineered for dominance.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Sign in to execute your mission!\n", "css": "margin-top: 3.25rem;\nheight: 5.279999732971191rem;\nfont-size: 1rem;"}
                  ]},
                {"format": "Powered by 461 © 2025", "css": "flex: 0 0 auto;\nheight: 1.5rem;\nwidth: 46.25rem;"}
